      <title>德意志银行首席财务官认为交易和咨询业务将实现“健康”增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/deutsche-bank-investment-bank-seeing-healthy-growth-cfo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行首席财务官詹姆斯冯莫尔特克表示，德意志银行本季度投资银行业务增长相当“健康”，交易、发起和咨询业务均比去年同期有所增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/deutsche-bank-investment-bank-seeing-healthy-growth-cfo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 08:13:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
